While researching this topic, what really surprised me was how easily people can fall into cyber fraud, especially UPI scams. I always thought these things happen only when someone is careless, but I realized that even simple actions like clicking a link or following instructions on a call can lead to losing money. It was also surprising to know that students are often targeted because we use digital apps so frequently but don’t always think about the risks.
After learning all this, one habit I want to change is being more careful while using online payment apps. Earlier, I didn’t always pay attention to small details, but now I will make sure to check everything properly before making any payment. This has made me more aware and responsible while using the internet.
